(121 So. 918) A. D. STALCUP, etc., v. BIRMINGHAM REAL ESTATE & INVESTMENT CO. (6 Div. 312.) Supreme Court of Alabama. March 28, 1929. G. M. Edmonds, of Birmingham, for appellant. Woodall & Patrick, of Birmingham, for appellee. . ’ SAYRE, THOMAS, and BROWN, JJ., concur.

ANDERSON, C. J. Reversed and remanded.
